      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of its age and regular use. While the mechanical components, including the engine and transmission, are dependable and the car remains a reliable daily driver, the exterior features several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery shows visible wear and a few stains, though all essential electronics and climate controls are fully functional. This is an honest, high-mileage vehicle that is mechanically sound but would benefit from some cosmetic attention.",
