      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sophisticated styling. This unit has undergone a comprehensive professional inspection to ensure peak performance and road-readiness. Meticulously maintained and showing clear pride of ownership, it offers an exceptional balance of performance and long-term value. We invite discerning buyers to experience the superior handling and refined interior that define this model\u2019s enduring appeal.",
