    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "For sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six. This example is mechanically sound, with the high-revving valvetrain recently shimmed to spec and a VANOS system that remains quiet and responsive across the powerband. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip differential with no excessive lash. The chassis has been proactively addressed with subframe reinforcement plates, ensuring structural rigidity during spirited cornering. Suspension components feature refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the factory-intended kinematic balance. While the exterior shows minor evidence of its 8,000 RPM pedigree, the longitudinal performance and throttle response remain razor-sharp. A turn-key enthusiast machine ready for the apex.",
      "price": 38500.0,
